Package ariba.ui.aribaweb.core Description

The core component engine of AW.

Key classes include AWComponent, AWRequestContext, AWRequest, AWResponse, AWSession, AWApplication, and AWDirectAction.

Core also includes basic "elements" for control and dynamic html rendering, including a:If, a:For, a:IncludeComponent, a:GenericElement, and a:GenericContainer,

Finally, core contains the foundation of AW's automatic incremental/dynamic refresh capability: a:RefreshRegion.

See Also:
ariba.ui.aribaweb.html
